      <h1>artifact rule</h1>

      <p>
        An artifact belongs in datapanick when you can answer both questions:
      </p>

      <ul class="list">
        <li>What signal produced this feeling?</li>
        <li>Where did meaning fail to translate?</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Artifacts may be incomplete. They may contradict one another.
        They may refuse narrative closure.
      </p>

      <p>
        What they may not do is pretend immediacy.
